  <title translate="true">MotionDesigner User Interface</title>
  <meta name="DESCRIPTION" translate="true" value="Use MotionDeisgner to design complex motion for multi-axis machines. The motions can have any number of segments. There are many different Motion-Laws you can select. Many of the Motion-Laws have different segment-parameters that can modify their functionality." />
